#: en/content/installation/source.xml:111
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "OTRS needs some additional Perl modules, as described in Table 3-1. If "
#| "you install OTRS from source, you will have to install these modules "
#| "manually. This can be done either with the package manager of your Linux "
#| "distribution (<application>yast</application>, <application>apt-get</"
#| "application>) or, as described in this section, through the Perl shell "
